Software Meevo is described as Meevo is the award-winning salon and spa software powered by Millennium built specifically for the beauty industry to simplify client management, improve business operations, and enhance your marketing strategies. Crush your goals and grow your business in one completely customizable, easy-to-use platform with a 98.5% positive support rating from more than 350,000 users. You'll gain best-in-class, 5-star support from the moment you join the Meevo Community.. Pricing described as Meevo pricing tiers are dependent on the number of users required. Pricing starts at $149/month for up to 10 users and scales as follows:

Grow: $149/month for up to 10 users and 2,500 text messages.

Pro: $269/month for up to 25 users and 5,000 text messages.

Powerhouse: $419/month for unlimited users and 10,000 text messages.

Enterprise: Custom enterprise plans are available upon request. and a target audience Salon, spa, and medical spa businesses looking for easy-to-use software that provides everything needed to streamline operations, manage clients and grow. 
